name: Fastify Microservice Template
desc: A lightweight, scalable API template for building high-performance microservices using Fastify and Prisma ORM. Designed for rapid backend development, it features modular routing, environment-based configuration, centralized error handling, and a clean project structure—ideal for building modern RESTful APIs with Node.js and Prisma.

name: Real Estate Listing Website
desc: A dynamic, responsive real estate platform built with JavaScript, PHP, Blade, and CoffeeScript—designed to help users easily browse, search, and inquire about properties. The site features a clean UI with modern CSS styling, interactive JavaScript components, and Blade templating for server-side rendering. Built on a robust PHP backend, it supports property filtering, agent contact, image galleries, and location-based search—perfect for real estate agencies or property management businesses.
